quran[30]{c,v,t,f}:
  68,37,"Kapena nkwete chitabu chankusoomaga nkati mwakwe."
  68,38,"Yanti chisimu nkwete kupata mu lyele (lisiku lya Kiyamalyo) yankuisaka?"
  68,39,"Kapena nkwete ŵanganyammwe ilanga Kukwetu yakuja kwika mpaka lisiku lya Kiyama, yakuti chisimu ŵanganyammwe chinchipata yankulijiilanyichisya?"
  69,34,"Soni nganaŵa jwakuchisya yagaliisya masikini."
  69,35,"Basi nganakola jwalakwejo lelo kwekuno nsyoŵe (jwakunkamuchisya)."
  69,36,"Namuno yakulya ikaŵeje uwowu (wakusulula m’maŵanga ga ŵandu ŵa ku Moto)."
  70,28,"Chisimu ilagasyo ya M’mbuje gwao nganiyiŵa yati kulupuka nayo (mundu jwakusakala)."
  70,29,"Ni aŵala ŵanya ŵaakuŵa ali nkuugosa utukani wao (pangatenda yansese). ",footnotes:1:[Akusimulila Sahl bin Sa‘d رضى الله عنه yanti : Ntenga jwa Allah ﷺ jwatite: “ Jwalijose jwatasunjile une malo gagali chilikati cha ndewu ni masharubu (pakamwa), ni malo gagaili chilikati changongolo syakwe (utukani), une tinansunjile Mbepo.” (Swahîh Al-Bukhârî, Hadith No.6109).]
  70,30,"Ikaŵeje kwa achiŵammakwao kapena (mateeka) gagapatile magasa gao gakun'dyo; basi chisimu ŵanganyao (pa yalakweyo) nganaŵa agambidwe."
  71,25,"Ligongo lya ilemwa yao ŵamisyidwe (m’mesi) ni kwinjisyidwa ku Moto, soni nganansimana jwalijose jwanti ni kwakulupusya jwangaŵaga Allah."
  71,26,"Soni Nuhu jwatite: “Ambuje ŵangu! Ngasimunneka pa chilambo pano ata jumo mwa makafiliŵa.”"
  71,27,"“Chisimu Mmwe naga nkwaleka ŵanganyao taŵe ali nkwasokonesya achikapolo Ŵenu, soni ŵanyao ngaŵa nkuŵeleka (mwanache jwambone) ikaŵeje jwakusakasya nnope, jwakanila kusyene.”"
  72,22,"Jilani: “Chisimu une ngaŵa nkuunjokola jwalijose (ku ipotesi ya) kuumila kwa Allah (naga ndili nannyosisye), soni ngaŵa nkupata kwakutilila kwangaŵaga Kukwakwe."
  72,23,"Ikaŵeje kulungusya (yakuona) ya kuumila kwa Allah ni utenga Wakwe (gele ni machili gangwete une), sano jwatannyosye Allah ni Ntenga Jwakwe ﷺ; basi chisimu uŵele wakwe jwalakwejo moto wa Jahannama, chakaŵe ŵandamo mwalakwemo yaka-yaka.”"
  72,24,"Kwikanila ndema jataachiiwona yaakuŵa ali nkupedwa chilanga (cha kwika kwakwe), pele nipatachimamyilila (yanti) ana ŵani ŵaakwete nkwaakamuchisya jwangali machili ni ŵaali chiŵalanjilo channono."
  73,16,"Nambo Afiriauna ŵannyosyisye Ntengajo, basi ni twaakwembekenye ni ilagasyo yakandapala kusyene."
  73,17,"Ana chin'digose chinauli (ku ipotesi) naga nkulikanila Lisiku lyalichitendekasya ŵanache kola wuuli?"
  73,18,"Liwunde lichipasuka mu lyele Lisikuli (ligongo lya kogoya kwakwe), chilanga Chakwe (Allah) chichiŵa chakutendekwa (mwangalepeleka)."
  74,13,"Ni ŵanache ŵakuŵanajo."
  74,14,"Ni nankolochesye (ndamo jakwe) kunkolochesya kwambone nnope."
  74,15,"Panyuma pakwe jukolaga tama janti ndili nan'jonjechesye."
  75,10,"Lyele lisikulyo mundu tachiti: “Kwakutilila ni kwapi?”"
  75,11,"Iyayi, pangali kwakutilila."
  75,12,"Kwa Ambuje ŵenupe (Allah) lyele lisikulyo nikuchipelela kwakuujila."
  76,4,"Chisimu Uwwe twalinganyichisye achimakafili malundelunde ga unyolo, ni makongwa kwisa soni Moto Wakulapuka."
  76,5,"Chisimu atenda ngoto chakamweje chipanda (chankologo) chakuwanganyichisya chakwe (nkologowo) chigakaŵeje (mesi ga) Kaafuura."
  76,6,"(Kaafuurajo ni) tutumule jwachakamwejemo achikapolo ŵa Allah, chakam'bumyeje (palipose pachakasacheje) kaumye kangasausya."
  77,1,"Ngujilumbila mbungo jajikupuga mwakuyana."
  77,2,"Ni mbungo jajikupuga mwa chimbunga."
  77,3,"Ni mbungo jajikwenesya (mawunde kwisa soni wula) mu kajenesye (kaasachile Allah)."